metadata.description:
2009, dads apple imac & a laptop mic. "Electric Wind" is where it all began.


This was my first electronic demo that I made using Ableton Live in 2009...it's raw, unedited & brings back so many fond memories of early self discovery <3



Enjoy
x

lyrics.text:
Electric wind, tonight we meet
Foresee the truth, I'd move for you

Moving seas, we spin out of control
Collecting pools of fear, I lose the need

Falling to pieces, collecting peace of mind
Doubtful in the end, tryin' to start tryin' to turn a bend

Make sense of time, before it slows
Slowly dissolves, more so than my despair

We plead and then we play
Folding into the ground
I carry the wood and the glue to mend this broken dollhouse

Falling to pieces, collecting peace of mind
Doubtful in the end, tryin' to start tryin' to turn a bend
